{"type": "article", "id": 16416, "title": "走廊自行车", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-22T07:01:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060042219VqL0rW4Bx8mnepY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t荷兰设计师 David Roman 在荷兰设计周上带来了这把走廊自行车。采用合金铝制框架，重量轻且体型小巧。它的折叠方式是旋转车把手和脚踏板，使它尽可能收成一个狭长的体型，能直接扛在肩上或挂在墙上。在墙上配上一个木质的挂钩，托住车架，自行车立刻成为家中的装饰。 <a href=\"http://www.droman.co/bicycle/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143709BkZjE9Y0zIvKeXN5.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"655\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.8007335\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143710xY2cGh6AgoDfKByL.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"654\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614371112IQdm8cWBa0s5xA.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"655\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.8007335\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143712kf3aQxh01Bgzbo6P.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"518\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63325183\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}